title: In case two or more registered developers submit a scheme on same land; then such proposals will be scrutinized chronologically on the basis of the land development rights acquired by the developer and the consent of hutment dwellers
clause_text: In case two or more registered developers submit a scheme on same land; then such proposals will be scrutinized chronologically on the basis of the land development rights acquired by the developer and the consent of hutment dwellers.
